        <h3>Problem</h3>
        <p>Bitcoin ATMs offer a convenient and easy to use physical platform for cryptocurrency users looking to
          purchase Bitcoin with cash. These kiosks serve a market that includes unbanked and underbanked individuals who
          either have no access to credit/debit cards, or simply do not believe in traditional banking. </p>
        <p>One of Bitstop’s chief challenges was effectively targeting and educating these users through its website,
          and then directing them to one of Bitstop’s ATM locations. The company’s original website, however, didn’t
          correctly address these challenges. It was not mobile friendly, had a muted color palette, included outdated
          information, and used graphic material not reflecting Bitstop’s latest and current products or how to use
          them.&nbsp;</p>
